{"tid":227969,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解愈發達愈唔開心?","createTime":"2017-05-03T14:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T14:47:39.000Z","uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af0a041e562b045e2fb6a2b63e41d2cee51ea210","tid":227969,"uid":82344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"愈發達嘅地方就愈多第三產業,愈少第一第二產業,即係愈多服務業,愈少農業工業。<br />\n<br />\n做服務業又要睇人面口,又要受氣,通常只係一個小職員，睇唔到自己工作有咩好實質嘅成果,咪又係幫老闆賺左錢,做又36,唔做又36,個人冇咩成就感。<br />\n<br />\n做農夫雖然體力勞動,但係種出黎見到食到。工業唔係流水線式,係自家工場嗰種感覺自己有一門手藝嘅自豪感。<br />\n<br />\n唔淨係錢,份工都好大影響。"},{"pid":"8ad10bdfd0db1fd905bc0b12be2654b0f293b8d7","tid":227969,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"經濟發展模式唔同<br />\n得小部份人享受到經濟發展嘅成果"},{"pid":"fc25b178132a93669ec3d9decc545a4c6a3d7209","tid":227969,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經濟發展模式唔同<br />\n得<span style=\"color: red;\">少</span>部份人享受到經濟發展嘅成果</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad79dea730c03f325d1cfab8494b67868ed68e06","tid":227969,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>經濟發展模式唔同<br />\n得<span style=\"color: red;\">少</span>部份人享受到經濟發展嘅成果</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小部分 先啱<br />\n<br />\n虧你仲話係語文系教授<br />\n<br />\n利申: AB, AM, PhD in Linguistic, DPhil, DLitt"},{"pid":"6829716672cd19fb2812ed51e66db69a0925a9a7","tid":227969,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>經濟發展模式唔同<br />\n得<span style=\"color: red;\">少</span>部份人享受到經濟發展嘅成果</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小部分 先啱<br />\n<br />\n虧你仲話係語文系教授<br />\n<br />\n利申: AB, AM, PhD in